metadata.name: Raised & Seated Cleveland
metadata.description: Portrait of the greatest basketball player of our generation. There will only be 4 variations of this NFT.  There are currently 4 NFT variations of these portraits: the original, and one for each team he has played for. Each word and illustration was carefully chosen to display the characteristics and stats and history of LBJ. I may create one more variation  for his final chapter if he signs with a new team which would bring the total to 5 NFTs.
